These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, tea, milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, hip-hop, indie
1. the fan of hip-hop is the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking milk is between the fan of indie and the person drinking tea##2
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | tea | milk | water |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop     | dubstep    | indie   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, dancing, gardening
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, architect, musician
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the musician is between the accountant and the person who's hobby is chess##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | chess    | gardening        | dancing |
| Job     | architect | musician | accountant         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk, milk
3 different pets are kept: mouse, lizard, frog
1. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the owner of the lizard and the person drinking milk##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | hot-chocolate     | milk |
| Pet        | lizard  | frog | mouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, trance, indie
3 different pets are kept: ferret, rabbit, lizard
1. the fan of ambient is the owner of the ferret##1
2. the fan of indie is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the ferret##2
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Music-Genre   | trance  | indie     | ambient |
| Pet           | rabbit | lizard | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, rock-climbing, drawing
3 different pets are kept: frog, mouse, rabbit
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | drawing     | woodworking |
| Pet     | rabbit    | frog | mouse    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, german, chinese
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: water-polo, tennis, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the chinese and the turkish##2
2. the turkish is the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the german is on the right of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | turkish  | german   | chinese        |
| Sport         | tennis | water-polo | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: mango, watermelon, grapefruit
There are 3 different nationalities: mexican, polish, british
1. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person eating mango##1
2. the mexican is between the person eating grapefruit and the polish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | watermelon  | mango  | grapefruit |
| Nationality   | polish | mexican | british     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, disaster, fantasy
There are 3 different nationalities: nigerian, american, dutch
1. the person watching disaster movies is the dutch##1
2. the american is between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching fantasy movies##2
3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy   | adventure  | disaster  |
| Nationality   | nigerian | american | dutch |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, soccer, skiing
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, taxi, ship
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person driving the train is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person driving the taxi##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | skiing | sailing | soccer  |
| Transport   | ship    | train        | taxi |

