.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, cola, tea
There 3 different types of food: cherry, pumpkin, watermelon
1. the person eating watermelon is between the person drinking cola and the person eating cherry##2
2. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | cola | water      | tea      |
| Food       | pumpkin  | watermelon | cherry |

