The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, golf, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is cricket is between the italian and the german##2
2. the italian is on the far left##1
3. the italian is the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | italian | indonesian   | german   |
| Sport         | snowboarding  | cricket | golf |

