.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, coffee, almond-milk
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, soul, pop
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking almond-milk and the fan of soul##2
3. the fan of metal is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | coffee   | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | pop  | metal | soul   |

 